2011-05-15T19:31:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-15/djokovic-defeats-nadal-in-rome-masters-final-to-remain-unbeaten-in-2011.html
Novak Djokovic of  Serbia  beat  Spain ’s
Rafael Nadal 6-4, 6-4 in the final of tennis’s Rome Masters
today to maintain his unbeaten run in 2011.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
